00/wsj_0036:Meanwhile, the National Association of Purchasing Management said its latest survey indicated that the manufacturing economy contracted in October for the sixth consecutive month.
00/wsj_0036:The purchasing managers, however, also said that orders turned up in October after four months of decline. 
