00/wsj_0036:For the first nine months of the year, total construction spending ran about 2% above last year's level. 
00/wsj_0036:Although the purchasing managers' index continues to indicate a slowing economy, it isn't signaling an imminent recession, said Robert Bretz, chairman of the association's survey committee and director of materials management at Pitney Bowes Inc., Stamford, Conn.
00/wsj_0036:He said the index would have to be in the low 40% range for several months to be considered a forecast of recession. 
