00/wsj_0051:NEC, one of its largest domestic competitors, said it bid one yen in two separate public auctions since 1987.
00/wsj_0051:The Ministry of International Trade and Industry summoned executives from the companies to "make sure they understood" the concern about such practices, according to a government spokesman. "These cases lead to the loss of the firms' social and international credibility," a ministry statement said. 
