00/wsj_0071:Image has, of course, a great deal to do with what sells and what doesn't, and it can't be forced.
00/wsj_0071:It's hardly a question of quality -- the 1982 Salon is a beautiful wine, but, as Mr. Pratt noted, people have their own ideas about value. 
00/wsj_0071:It's interesting to find that a lot of the expensive wines aren't always walking out the door.
