02/wsj_0204:The new "social choice" fund will shun securities of companies linked to South Africa, nuclear power and in some cases, Northern Ireland.
02/wsj_0204:Sixty percent of the fund will be invested in stocks, with the rest going into bonds or short-term investments. 
