04/wsj_0409:Nearly half of those who joined health clubs said they didn't use their membership as often as they planned.
04/wsj_0409:Even so, the Association of Quality Clubs, a health-club trade group in Boston, says membership revenues will rise about 5% this year from last year's $5 billion.
