08/wsj_0800:Acquired from Carisbrook Holdings U.K. Ltd., a company owned by Australian financier Robert Holmes a Court, the stake was apparently the first of its kind for Aska, an entity separate from Aichi.
08/wsj_0800:And the acquisition, which made Aska one of Christies' top five shareholders, left many people wondering who this man was and what his intentions were. 
