08/wsj_0847:The results have led analysts to predict that the company's 1989 cash flow will be more than 20% ahead of the debt-coverage ratio required by RJR's banks. 
08/wsj_0847:Much of KKR's financing for the RJR buy-out is with so-called payment-in-kind debt, notes that accumulate interest in more notes and don't require cash payments for several years.
