09/wsj_0989:At Air Products, meanwhile, the mailroom staff opens junk mail and often throws it away -- even if addressed to an individual. "If they get 50 packets of something, they open one, see what it says, throw 48 away and send two to people or departments they think are appropriate," a spokesman says. 
