10/wsj_1002:This is no longer true because of Campeau's massive debt load. 
10/wsj_1002:"The few million dollars I could lose today is nothing against what I could lose on the spring line," says Mr. Levy, who estimates that Campeau stores will sell $25 million worth of his clothes this year. "I'm buying fabric right now for clothes which I may not be paid for until April or May.
