11/wsj_1145:Assuming full operation of the Seabrook nuclear power plant, which is completed but isn't yet operating, equity holders would receive up to $500 million in cash, preferred stock and new 10-year Seabrook bonds.
11/wsj_1145:In addition, Northeast promised the State of New Hampshire that rate increases would be limited to 5.5% annually for seven years.
