11/wsj_1146:On it, a quarter of the country's 39 million people produce three-quarters of its grain, beef, eggs and milk, and nine-tenths of its fruit, vegetables and potatoes.
11/wsj_1146:Like the Roman Catholic Church, the Polish peasant is a pillar of the nation.
