11/wsj_1171:Benjamin Jacobson & Sons has been the New York Stock Exchange specialist firm in charge of trading stock in UAL Corp. and its predecessors since the early 1930s. 
11/wsj_1171:At first UAL didn't open because of an order imbalance.
11/wsj_1171:But we like to call it 'controlled chaos, '" said 47-year-old Robert J. Jacobson Jr., grandson of the firm's founder.
