13/wsj_1312:The issue is the first by Ford Motor Credit, a unit of Ford Motor Co., and the second largest in the four-year history of the $45 billion asset-backed market.
13/wsj_1312:The largest issue was a $4 billion offering of auto-loan securities by General Motors Acceptance Corp. in 1986.
