14/wsj_1418:A spokesman for the city wouldn't confirm the size of the bond issue, but did say that a general obligation offering is in the works and should be priced sometime in the next two weeks, before the November mayoral election. (General obligation bonds are backed by the city's overall revenues and credit.) 
14/wsj_1418:Although many investors were aware that a bond offering was being scheduled, many expected a much smaller amount of bonds to be sold.
