15/wsj_1561:Terms weren't disclosed for the plant, which will have annual capacity of 600,000 tons. 
15/wsj_1561:The move by the nation's largest steelmaker follows a string of earlier announcements by other major steel companies.
15/wsj_1561:They note that most of the new plants will come on line in 1992, when the current import trade restraint program ends, which could result in more imports. 
