18/wsj_1874:Municipal bonds ended about 1/8 to 3/8 point lower, hurt by the circulation of two "bid-wanted" lists totaling $655 million. 
18/wsj_1874:Meanwhile, some California issues were down a touch more than the broad market, but traders said there hadn't been much investor selling because of the quake. 
