19/wsj_1903:She will oversee Working Woman, Working Mother and Success magazines, and retain her post as publisher of Working Woman. 
19/wsj_1903:The sale price of McCall's -- twice what Mr. Lang originally paid for it -- will finance Lang Communications' buy-back of Time Warner's 50% interest in Working Woman and Working Mother.
19/wsj_1903:There is plenty of work to be done on what we have." 
