20/wsj_2013:Mr. Noriega also conveyed intelligence from his spy operation inside the Nicaraguan capital of Managua.
20/wsj_2013:And on at least one occasion, in the spring of 1985, he helped arrange a sabotage attack on a Sandinista arsenal in Nicaragua.
