23/wsj_2359:Approximately 85% of the total consisted of nonperforming commercial real estate assets.
23/wsj_2359:CityFed added that significant additional loan-loss provisions may be required by federal regulators as part of the current annual examination of City Federal Savings Bank, CityFed's primary subsidiary, based in Somerset, N.J. City Federal operates 105 banking offices in New Jersey and Florida. 
