23/wsj_2361:Another, "Jeux Sans Frontieres," where villagers from assorted European countries make fools of themselves performing pointless tasks, is a hit in France.
23/wsj_2361:The cream of the British crop, the literary dramas that are shown on U.S. public television as "Masterpiece Theater," make up a relatively small part of British air time.
23/wsj_2361:Most British programming is more of an acquired taste.
