23/wsj_2372:To the detriment of many low-income people, efforts to boost Medicaid funding, especially in rural areas, also were stricken. 
23/wsj_2372:It no longer includes a plan that would have repealed what remains of the completed-contract method of accounting, which is used by military contractors to reduce their tax burden.
