23/wsj_2399:The issue, which is puttable back to the company at par on Oct. 15, 1999, was priced at a spread of 50 basis points above the Treasury's 10-year note.
23/wsj_2399:Centel Capital Corp. -- $150 million of 9% debentures due Oct. 15, 2019, priced at 99.943 to yield 9.008%.
