23/wsj_2399:The offering, Series 102, backed by Freddie Mac 8 1/2% securities with a weighted average remaining term to maturity of 28.4 years, was priced before the market's afternoon surge.
23/wsj_2399:Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corp. -- $300 million of Remic mortgage securities offered by Citicorp Securities Markets Inc.
23/wsj_2399:Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corp. -- $200 million of stripped mortgage securities underwritten by BT Securities Corp.
23/wsj_2399:Freddie Mac said the principal-only securities were priced at 58 1/4 to yield 8.45%, assuming an average life of eight years and a prepayment of 160% of the PSA model.
