24/wsj_2462:Mr. Magarity said Chase hopes to assemble an international group of banks in the lending syndicate, including some of U.S. and Japanese banks with which China Resources has had a strong relationship in recent years. "Right now we think we can successfully syndicate this loan because of China Resources' name," he said. 
24/wsj_2462:Indeed, the reputations of China Resources and Citic played a significant role in the decisions.
